snippet.title: Tempopo Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist us on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/318840/Tempopo/

Tempopo is a contemplative puzzle game of planning and execution. Guide your Tempopo to rescue musical flowers across imaginative sky islands and arrange them in your own melodic garden. Take your time placing instructions and watch the harmonious or hilarious results of your decisions.

Join our mailing list: https://www.tempopogame.com/
Follow us on Twitter: https://twitter.com/tempopogame

Coming to Windows/OSX/Linux, Nintendo Switch, Xbox One, and XBox Series X/S.

Music by Jeff van Dyck, featuring vocals by Angela van Dyck and Eneteti Turnbull.
